# API keys — matches at any depth (root, or script-local under .claude/skills/panel/)
.env

# Panel client state (per-working-directory).
.claude/panel_state.json

# Generated signal files and archived passes — the example ships with an empty
# episode-1/ (just task.md); everything else is produced by running the harness.
harness/episodes/*/plan-signal.json
harness/episodes/*/work-signal.json
harness/episodes/*/forensics-signal.json
harness/episodes/*/review-signal.json
harness/episodes/*/pass-*/

# Worker artifacts live alongside signals inside each episode dir. Recipients
# will produce their own — uncomment if you want them tracked during dev:
# harness/episodes/*/*.md
# harness/episodes/*/*.json
# (The two lines above are too broad and would ignore task.md — leaving commented.)
